    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a generous drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, drain your<strong> jumbo prawns</strong>, then add them to the pan with the <strong>halved cherry tomatoes </strong>and cook for 3 min</p>",
