      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained spaghetti </strong>to the pan with a splash of the<strong> starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Cook for 1 min further, stirring until the sauce thickens – this is your <strong>chilli, garlic & jumbo prawn spaghetti</strong></p><p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
